  <brief_title>Vaginal Cleansing at Cesarean Delivery to Reduce Infection: A Randomized, Controlled Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Vaginal Cleansing at Cesarean Delivery to Reduce Infection: A Randomized, Controlled Trial</official_title>
